data.description: Welcome to this stunning single-story gem in Pleasant Valley. Built in 2019, this home boasts elegance & functionality A luxurious Next Gen suite w. private entry. Ideal for extended family, suite includes bed, bath, kitchenette & living area. This addition ensures privacy & independence. Home includes 3 beds & 2.5 baths. The heart of this home is undoubtedly the gourmet kitchen, featuring a central kitchen island, exquisite granite countertops, and top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances. Water softener & Remote gate entry. Whether you're an amateur chef or just love to entertain, this kitchen will inspire your culinary creativity. The 2-car garage and RV parking w. convenient side gate provide ample space for your vehicles and outdoor toys. The home also boasts modern conveniences like home automation, ensuring your comfort and security are at your fingertips. A contemporary design, luxurious finishes, and practical layout, it offers a lifestyle that's both elegant and functional.
